title: New Instagram account
description: New instagram account for shark and ray #scicomm in Brazil.
contents: Check out the Instagram account @elasmos_br to find out about new papers about sharks and rays from Brazil! The account has daily posts from Monday to Friday, recorded live interviews with Brazilian researchers about a myriad of topics.
